column2: SELECT top # sp.plate, sp.mjd, sp.fiberid, sp.specobjid, sp.bestobjid, s.elodiervfinal, s.teffadop, s.fehadop, s.loggadop,  sp.class, sp.subclass, sp.ra, sp.dec  FROM sppParams as s JOIN SpecObjAll as sp ON s.specobjid = sp.specobjid WHERE s.teffadop between # and # AND sp.class = &&& AND sp.ra > # and sp.ra < #  AND  sp.dec > # and sp.dec < #
